# The Cloudflare Origin Certificate + private key live here ON THE VPS (secrets).
# Expected files (placed by hand during deploy — see docs/deploy-runbook.md):
#   pitchup.online.pem   (origin certificate)
#   pitchup.online.key   (origin private key)
# Ignore everything in this folder except this file, so the directory still
# exists in the repo (Caddy mounts it read-only) but no secret is ever committed.
*
!.gitignore
